### Interactive API Tests
### Tests for InteractiveController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Get pending questions
### Returns all pending questions that need user response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/questions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Reply to a question
### Sends a reply to a pending question
POST http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/questions/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_id": "question_uuid",
  "response": "Yes, proceed with the operation"
}

###

### Reply to a question with option selection
### Sends a reply selecting a specific option
POST http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/questions/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_id": "question_uuid",
  "option_id": "option_1"
}

###

### Get pending permissions
### Returns all pending permission requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/permissions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Reply to a permission request
### Sends a reply to a pending permission request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/permissions/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission_id": "permission_uuid",
  "allow": true,
  "remember": false
}

###

### Respond to a permission request
### Alternative endpoint for responding to permission requests
POST http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/permissions/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "permission_uuid",
  "action": "allow"
}

###

### Deny a permission request
### Denies a pending permission request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/interactive/permissions/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "permission_uuid",
  "action": "deny"
}

###
